# The committed demo single-files (demo/safeseed-demo.html, demo/safeseed-generator.html)
# are rebuilt and diffed by CI to catch staleness. Pin all HTML to LF so that rebuild
# diffs cleanly across OSes (vite/esbuild emit LF; this stops a Windows checkout's CRLF
# from showing as spurious drift).
*.html text eol=lf
